<h2><a class="mozTocH2" name="mozTocId97661"></a>0.3 Allah is responsible for disbelief</h2>
</div>
<ul class="_33MEMislY0GAlB78wL1_CR">
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://quranx.com/2.7" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Allah seals disbelievers from belief</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://quranx.com/39.36" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Allah causes people to be astray</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://quranx.com/74.31" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Allah chooses which people he wants to believe or disbelieve</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://quranx.com/6.88" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Allah guides whomever he wants to be guided</a> ———————————————————————————</p>
