<h2><a class="mozTocH2" name="mozTocId121476"></a>1.1 Islamic Mistreatment of Women</h2>
</div>
<div class="_2UlSUuiYR4BRv_FiLxCcu9">
<h3><a class="mozTocH3" name="mozTocId394064"></a>Restrictive female dress code</h3>
</div>
<ul class="_33MEMislY0GAlB78wL1_CR">
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/bukhari:4758" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">The Qur’anic Hijab demands women cover their faces</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/muslim:645a" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">The hijab causes a woman to be unrecognisable</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/bukhari:5936" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad curses women who artificially extend their hair</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/urn/730040" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad curses women who remove hair from their faces for beautification</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/bukhari:146" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Umar harasses muhammad’s wife for not being veiled</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/ibnmajah:1989" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad curses the woman who plucks her eyebrows</a> ———————————————————————————</p>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="_2UlSUuiYR4BRv_FiLxCcu9">
<h3><a class="mozTocH3" name="mozTocId967695"></a>Female subservience to men</h3>
</div>
<ul class="_33MEMislY0GAlB78wL1_CR">
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://quranx.com/4.34" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Allah says righteous women are devoutly obedient to their husbands</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://quranx.com/2.228" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Allah affirms that men are degrees above women</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/bukhari:3237" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">A Wife must always be available for sex or she gets cursed by angels</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/mishkat:3255" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad deems it appropriate for a wife to prostrate to her husband</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/ibnmajah:1853" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad says a wife must fulfill her husband’s desire for intimacy even if she is on a camel saddle</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/ibnmajah:1882" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Women must rely on the men in their lives to choose their husbands for them</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/bukhari:5195" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad says a woman cannot keep voluntary Fasts without the husband’s permission</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/bukhari:5195" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad says women cannot let anyone enter the home without her husband’s permission</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/bukhari:5137" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad says silence is consent</a> ———————————————————————————</p>
</li>
