</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/muslim:1836" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad says be obedient to your Ruler even if the Ruler is being unfair to you</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/riyadussalihin:668" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad says obey your Ruler even if they are not giving you what is due to you</a> ———————————————————————————</p>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="WFFrvt6_3z5B7MBcYKr8U">
<h2><a class="mozTocH2" name="mozTocId826482"></a>2.4 Killing dissenters, blasphemers, and mockers</h2>
</div>
<ul class="_33MEMislY0GAlB78wL1_CR">
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Asma_bint_Marwan" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad commands to kill Asma’ bint Marwan for making a poem mocking him</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/abudawud:4361" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad acquits a man who killed his concubine for insulting Muhammad</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/muslim:1801" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad commands his sahabah to kill a poet who insulted him</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
