<h2><a class="mozTocH2" name="mozTocId417896"></a>3.6 Islamic Historical Errors</h2>
</div>
<ul class="_33MEMislY0GAlB78wL1_CR">
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://quranx.com/5.116?Context=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Allah asserts that Christians believe that Mary is a divinity to be worshiped</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://quranx.com/9.30?Context=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Allah claims that Jews believe that Ezra is the son of god</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://quranx.com/19.7?Context=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Allah claims that no one had the name John before John the Baptist</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://quranx.com/12.41?Context=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Allah claims The Pharaoh crucified subjects, despite crucifixion being only invented a thousand of years later by Romans</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://sunnah.com/mishkat:753" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">Muhammad claims that Abraham and Solomon lived within 40 years of each other</a></p>
</li>
<li class="_3gqTEjt4x9UIIpWiro7YXz">
<p class="_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM"><a class="_3t5uN8xUmg0TOwRCOGQEcU" href="https://quranx.com/5.116" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">With no proof, and ignoring historical proof, Allah claims that Jesus never said to worship him</a> ———————————————————————————</p>
</li>
</ul>
